<title>USA: Arthuis, on dlr--markets should watch fundamentals.</title>
<headline>Arthuis, on dlr--markets should watch fundamentals.</headline>
<dateline>WASHINGTON 1997-04-28</dateline>
<text>
<p>French Finance Minister Jean Arthuis said on Monday that financial markets should take account of economic fundamentals.</p>
<p>He had been asked what he thought about a rise in the dollar since Sunday's talks between Group of Seven finance ministers and central bank heads.</p>
<p>&quot;They (markets) must take account of economic fundamentals,&quot; he told reporters.</p>
